ing%22%3EIn%20January%202006%20in%20New%20York%2C%20the%20patient%20of%20a%20well-known%20psychiatrist%20draws%20the%20face%20of%20a%20man%20that%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20appearing%20in%20her%20dreams.%20In%20more%20than%20one%20occasion%20that%20man%20has%20given%20her%20advice%20on%20her%20private%20life.%20The%20woman%20swears%20she%20has%20never%20met%20the%20man%20in%20her%20life.%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3Ch2%20class%3D%22wp-block-heading%22%3EThat%20portrait%20lies%20forgotten%20on%20the%20psychiatrist%E2%80%99s%20desk%20for%20a%20few%20days%20until%20one%20day%20another%20patient%20recognizes%20that%20face%20and%20says%20that%20the%20man%20has%20often%20visited%20him%20in%20his%20dreams.%20He%20also%20claims%20he%20has%20never%20seen%20that%20man%20in%20his%20waking%20life.%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3Ch2%20class%3D%22wp-block-heading%22%3EThe%20psychiatrist%20decides%20to%20send%20the%20portrait%20to%20some%20of%20his%20colleagues%20that%20have%20patients%20with%20recurrent%20dreams.%20Within%20a%20few%20months%2C%20four%20patients%20recognize%20the%20man%20as%20a%20frequent%20presence%20in%20their%20own%20dreams.%20All%20the%20patients%20refer%20to%20him%20as%26nbsp%3B%3Cstrong%3ETHIS%20MAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3Ch2%20class%3D%22wp-block-heading%22%3EFrom%20January%202006%20until%20today%2C%20at%20least%20%3Cs%3E2000%3C%2Fs%3E%208.000%20people%20have%20claimed%20they%20have%20seen%20this%20man%20in%20their%20dreams%2C%20in%20many%20cities%20all%20over%20the%20world%3A%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Berlin%2C%20Sao%20Paulo%2C%20Tehran%2C%20Beijing%2C%20Rome%2C%20Barcelona%2C%20Stockholm%2C%20Paris%2C%20New%20Dehli%2C%20Moskow%20etc.%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3Ch2%20class%3D%22wp-block-heading%22%3EAt%20the%20moment%20there%20is%20no%20ascertained%20relation%20or%20common%20trait%20among%20the%20people%20that%20have%20dreamed%20of%20seeing%20this%20man.%20Moreover%2C%20no%20living%20man%20has%20ever%20been%20recognized%20as%20resembling%20the%20man%20of%20the%20portrait%20by%20the%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20this%20man%20in%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3Ch2%20class%3D%22wp-block-heading%22%3EThe%20aim%20of%20this%20website%20is%3A%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%93%20to%20help%20those%20who%20have%20seen%20this%20man%20in%20their%20dreams%20and%20to%20foster%20communication%20among%20them%3B%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%93%20to%20understand%20who%20this%20man%20is%20and%20why%20he%20appears%20in%20an%20apparently%20pattern-less%20array%20of%20situations%20in%20the%20dreams%20of%20such%20diverse%20human%20subjects.%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%09%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%0A%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C!--%20.entry-content%20--%3E%0A%0A%09%09%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22screen-reader-text%22%20itemprop%3D%22datePublished%22%20itemtype%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fschema.org%2FDate%22%3E2023-02-26%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%0A%09%09%0A%09%3C%2Farticle%3E%3C!--%20.entry%20--%3E%0A%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C!--%20%23content-wrap%20--%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C!--%20%23content%20--%3E%0A%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%09%0A%09%3Caside%20id%3D%22sidebar-primary%22%20class%3D%22sidebar%20sidebar-primary%20hgrid-span-3%20layout-narrow-right%20%22%20role%3D%22complementary%22%20itemscope%3D%22itemscope%22%20itemtype%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fschema.org%2FWPSideBar%22%3E%0A%0A%09%09%3Csection%20id%3D%22nav_menu-3%22%20class%3D%22widget%20widget_nav_menu%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22menu-menu-1-container%22%3E%3Cul%20id%3D%22menu-menu-1%22%20class%3D%22menu%22%3E%3Cli%20class%3D%22menu-item%20menu-item-type-post_type%20menu-item-object-page%20menu-item-32%20menu-item-parent-archive%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisman.org%2Fnews%2F%22%3ENEWS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%20class%3D%22menu-item%20menu-item-type-post_type%20menu-item-object-page%20menu-item-31%20menu-item-parent-archive%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisman.org%2Fhistory%2F%22%3EHISTORY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%20class%3D%22menu-item%20menu-item-type-post_type%20menu-item-o